{"tid":1744234,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"秦國布吉島五日休息遊記","createTime":"2019-11-21T15:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:04:52.000Z","uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b233a63f4039f8a8979fc56ac97bd24efb47b357","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"早幾個禮拜去咗布吉休息 打返個靚遊記先！<br />\n<br />\n第一日：<br />\n夜晚先到布吉，係Klook訂咗車去巴東，平過係機場叫車，今次住Best Western，二百幾蚊晚幾抵屌，到酒店後落大雨，是但去七仔買啲宵夜返房食。"},{"pid":"fefa5bfefd79f8256903a75ab206f65870000e98","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"第二日：<br />\n朝早係酒店食早餐，幾撚難食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得個炒蛋可取，食完返房瞓多陣，兩點幾出門口去咗好出名嘅No.6 restaurant食，難食到仆街，好彩唔使排隊<br />\n<br />\n食完去沙灘行下，跟住去Jungceylon同新開嘅central百貨行，無咩嘢好行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有返酒店泳池遊個水<br />\n<br />\n夜晚出去食pizza company，食到好能飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過硬係覺得無曼谷嘅好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c8b82f0d94808e9dd71f1e212c33eb2c297487","tid":1744234,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"01fda0673acdbc99a32b46d5df4b91f99547d26a","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"第三日：<br />\n酒店早餐，食完返房瞓，下午搭巴士去布吉鎮，食網上好多人推薦嘅Kopitiam by wilai，正正常常，無大家講咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完行多陣就搭車返巴東，去咗let's relax做個泰式按摩，正正常常，唔覺同幾百銖嘅按摩店有好大分別<br />\n<br />\n晚餐去食Naughty Nuri&rsquo;s In The Forest，個ribs幾能正下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過個沙嗲雞好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完去酒吧街飲下酒，睇下囡就返歸"},{"pid":"7dc45d7a7b29ae15d5c7c84bf5a8e1c15266976f","tid":1744234,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"I've always thought Thailand is poorer than hong kong"},{"pid":"5064ccced42b4ee14f83989795b9f6cfba937d11","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"第四日：<br />\n訓能到一點幾先醒，去咗食間新開嘅餐廳，好似叫Tao，係No.6附近，估唔到有啲驚喜，個咖哩鴨同生菜包都幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完嘢就去沙灘游下水，跟住返酒店瞓晏覺<br />\n<br />\n晚餐去咗沙灘附近嘅Sultan Grill食，間嘢有土耳其嘢同印度嘢食，我兩種都有嗌，好食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完飯去Big C 買少少嘢就返酒店了"},{"pid":"1945708fab29d7ca09527108d7fda4dd22064339","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"第五日：<br />\n瞓醒覺就check out，係酒店附近是但食個快飯，就搭車去機場，坐飛機返戰場了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0329ba2fb50421018674f5ab1608ddcb0a62cd8","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"完！"},{"pid":"97106d6cc365c57eb7793865df76fd9efaa8d12d","tid":1744234,"uid":267632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"Following <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8816dd69726bcb093c90cfea684a1b949746ff0c","tid":1744234,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"冇相嘅喂<br />\n八月去完，覺得kata beach係最正最乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90c44d292f04af34a7906952380a7233d4230d5","tid":1744234,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8816dd69726bcb093c90cfea684a1b949746ff0c","tid":1744234,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:37:59.000Z",